  "text": "Furthermore, it is possible to introduce the time-dependence of the dynamical geometry for the Unruh vacuum (β(u) = 0) as a perturbation to this non-singular static geometry [CITATION_1] . [CITATION_2] As part of this work will be based on such a perturbation theory, we review the static geometry near the Schwarzschild radius [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
